    User story for Christmas Balance Pack purchase

    As a Call of Duty player, I explore and purchase the Christmas Balance Pack offer, so that I can enhance my gaming experience with an additional balance top-up for gameplay.

    Success definition: Given I am on the Legionfarm Call of Duty top offers page When I click on the 'Christmas Balance Pack' to view its details Then I should see the detailed description of the Christmas Balance Pack, including pricing and benefits, and I can proceed to purchase by clicking 'Buy now'.
